	</p><p class="cs709C557D"><div style="width:8.5pt;height:32pt;border-width:0.5pt;border-style:solid;border-color:Black;background-color:#FFFFFF;margin:0pt 9pt 0pt 9pt;padding:5pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;">
